OL,3,CInspectors told of racism and bullying
OL,4,Cat under-fire trust
OL,6,FInspectors have criticised leadership
OL,7,Fat an under-fire hospital trust after
OL,8,Freceiving complaints about racism and
OL,9,Fbullying.
OL,11,FThe Care Quality Commission (CQC)
OL,12,Fcarried out an inspection in June into
OL,13,Fhow Leeds Teaching Hospitals NHS Trust
OL,14,Fwas being run after concerns were
OL,15,Fraised about maternity and neonatal
OL,16,Fservices.
OL,18,FIt rated the trust's leadership as
OL,19,F"requires improvement".
