OL,3,CInspectors told of racism and bullying
OL,4,Cat under-fire trust
OL,6,FCQC director of operations Rob Assall
OL,7,Fsaid: "Leaders didn't always listen to
OL,8,Fconcerns, and some staff had negative
OL,9,Fexperiences when they voiced issues,
OL,10,Fwhich impacted their wellbeing and the
OL,11,Fquality of people's care.
OL,13,F"We received several in-depth accounts
OL,14,Ffrom staff of bullying and harassment
OL,15,Fin the workplace which provided
OL,16,Fevidence of behaviours which didn't
OL,17,Falign with the trust's values."
