OL,6,FTheir CQC's report said the complaints
OL,7,Fcame from a "relatively small number
OL,8,Fof staff" but included "all grades,
OL,9,Fdesignations and racial backgrounds of
OL,10,Fstaff".
OL,12,FLeeds was one of 14 maternity trusts
OL,13,Fnamed by the health secretary this
OL,14,Fmonth as facing investigation for
OL,15,F"systemic" failures in care.
