OL,6,FThe CQC had already downgraded its
OL,7,Frating of the trust's maternity
OL,8,Fprovision to "inadequate" after dozens
OL,9,Fof families affected by avoidable
OL,10,Fdeaths of babies or mothers called for
OL,11,Fan independent inquiry into alleged
OL,12,Ffailings.
OL,14,FThe trust runs Leeds General
OL,15,FInfirmary, St James's Hospital, Leeds
OL,16,FChildren's Hospital, Chapel Allerton
OL,17,FHospital, Wharfedale Hospital,
OL,18,FSeacroft Hospital and Leeds Dental
OL,19,FInstitute.
