OL,4,Cat under-fire trust
OL,6,FMr Assall said leaders were "aware of
OL,7,Fthe challenges they faced, however
OL,8,Fsome weren't as clear on how services
OL,9,Fcould be improved which negatively
OL,10,Fimpacted on how services were run".
OL,12,FHowever, the report noted that the
OL,13,Ftrust's leaders had "strong
OL,14,Frelationships with local and national
OL,15,Fpartnership organisations" and had
OL,16,Ftaken steps to improve the
OL,17,Feffectiveness of the board.
