OL,3,CInspectors told of racism and bullying
OL,4,Cat under-fire trust
OL,6,FThe trust's interim chief executive
OL,7,FBrendan Brown said the CQC received
OL,8,Freports of colleagues being subjected
OL,9,Fto "racist and bullying behaviours"
OL,10,Fand some staff "said their concerns
OL,11,Fweren't listened to".
OL,13,FHe added: "I want to sincerely
OL,14,Fapologise to those colleagues. We are
OL,15,Fcommitted to creating an inclusive
OL,16,Fworkplace where colleagues feel safe,
OL,17,Frespected, and supported, but we
OL,18,Fclearly have more work to do to ensure
OL,19,Fracism, discrimination and bullying
OL,20,Fhave no place in our hospitals."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G6/7
