OL,6,FHe said the trust would respond to the
OL,7,FCQC's concerns, adding: "We must focus
OL,8,Fon listening to our patients, our
OL,9,Fcommunities and our colleagues and be
OL,10,Fmore curious about what we're told. We
OL,11,Falso need to improve on how we act on
OL,12,Fwhat we hear.
OL,14,F"These changes need to happen quickly,
OL,15,Fas it is what the people we care for
OL,16,Fand work alongside expect and deserve."
